snippet.title: AMPlugged | gny - stories of home
snippet.description:
AMPlugged's back with its very first music video this year! 🎉

Presenting gny and his new song, stories of home!

Start 2018 right by exploring the beauty of Manila and discovering a new sound! 🤘🏻

Shot by Celina De Guzman and Fortunato Madamba
Edited by Celina De Guzman
Produced by Ninielle Pascual and John Montecillo
Special thanks to Juancho Luna and Regina Distor

snippet.title: AMPlugged | gny Interview
snippet.description:
AMPlugged's back with its very first artist: gny! What better way to de-stress this Christmas by discovering new artists and their music? Inspired by the hip-hop scene, get to know the magic behind gny and his sound.

Credits:
Shot and Edited by Regina Distor 
Recorded by Angel Codera
Animation by Ninielle Pascual
Thumbnail by Ninielle Pascual
Special thanks to Dane Santiago, Pancho Santos, Juancho Luna, and Angel Codera
